                     <interp inst="t18010520-9-off50" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010520-9-off50" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>
               feloniously receiving, on the <rs id="t18010520-9-cd51" type="crimeDate">28th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010520-9-off50 t18010520-9-cd51"></join>, two pigs, value 40s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18010520-9-victim92" type="victimName">
                        John 
