                  , where of John Allen, at the last Sessions, was convicted of stealing
            </rs>.(The record of the conviction of 
               <persName id="t18010520-9-person94">
                  John 
                  Allen
               <interp inst="t18010520-9-person94" type="surname" value="Allen"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010520-9-person94" type="given" value="John"></interp>
